t":"Author/Linhong Huang","line":91},{"title":"Author/Xiaoqiang Huang","target":"Author/Xiaoqiang Huang","line":92},{"title":"Author/Xiaoqiang Huang","target":"Author/Xiaoqiang Huang","line":93},{"title":"Author/Zhengyan Zhao","target":"Author/Zhengyan Zhao","line":94},{"title":"Author/Zefeng Zhao","target":"Author/Zefeng Zhao","line":95},{"title":"Author/Zefeng Zhao","target":"Author/Zefeng Zhao","line":96},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/he_structures_2017/he_structures_2017.pdf","line":98}],"metadata":{"id":"he_structures_2017","type":"article-journal","title":"Structures, biological activities, and industrial applications of the polysaccharides from Hericium erinaceus (Lion's Mane) mushroom: A review.","issued":{"date-parts":[[2017]]},"DOI":"10.1016/j.ijbiomac.2017.01.040","container-title":"International Journal of Biological Macromolecules","abstract":"Hericium erinaceus (Bull.) Pers., also known as Yamabushitake, Houtou and Lion's Mane, is capable of fortifying the spleen and nourishing the stomach, tranquilizing the mind, and fighting cancer. Over the past decade, it has been demonstrated that H. erinaceus polysaccharides possess various promising bioactivities, including antitumor and immunomodulation, anti-gastric ulcer, neuroprotection and neuroregeneration, anti-oxidation and hepatoprotection, anti-hyperlipidemia, anti-hyperglycemia, anti-fatigue and anti-aging. The purpose of the present review is to provide systematically reorganized information on extraction and purification, structure characteristics, biological activities, and industrial applications of H. erinaceus polysaccharides to support their therapeutic potentials and sanitarian functions.Copyright © 2017 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"He","given":"Xirui","literal":""},{"family":"He","given":"Xirui","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Xiaoxiao","literal":""},{"family":"Wang","given":"Xiaoxiao","literal":""},{"family":"Fang","given":"Jugao","literal":""},{"family":"Fang","given":"Jiacheng","literal":""},{"family":"Chang","given":"Yu Sun","literal":""},{"family":"Chang","given":"Yu","literal":""},{"family":"Ning","given":"Ning","literal":""},{"family":"Ning","given":"Ning","literal":""},{"family":"Guo","given":"Hao","literal":""},{"family":"Guo","given":"Hao","literal":""},{"family":"Huang","given":"Libei","literal":""},{"family":"Huang","given":"Linhong","literal":""},{"family":"Huang","given":"Xiaoqiang","literal":""},{"family":"Huang","given":"Xiaoqiang","literal":""},{"family":"Zhao","given":"Zhengyan","literal":""},{"family":"Zhao","given":"Zefeng","literal":""},{"family":"Zhao","given":"Zefeng","literal":""}],"citation-key":"he_structures_2017","year":"2017","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Structures, biological activities, and industrial applications of the polysaccharides from Hericium erinaceus (Lion's Mane) mushroom: A review."],"author-links":["[[Author/Xirui He]]","[[Author/Xirui He]]","[[Author/Xiaoxiao Wang]]","[[Author/Xiaoxiao Wang]]","[[Author/Jugao Fang]]","[[Author/Jiacheng Fang]]","[[Author/Yu Sun Chang]]","[[Author/Yu Chang]]","[[Author/Ning Ning]]","[[Author/Ning Ning]]","[[Author/Hao Guo]]","[[Author/Hao Guo]]","[[Author/Libei Huang]]","[[Author/Linhong Huang]]","[[Author/Xiaoqiang Huang]]","[[Author/Xiaoqiang Huang]]","[[Author/Zhengyan Zhao]]","[[Author/Zefeng Zhao]]","[[Author/Zefeng Zhao]]"],"attachment":["[[biblib/he_structures_2017/he_structures_2017.pdf|PDF]]"],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1t3xxr4","at":1774951893279}},"smart_blocks:Research/@he_structures_2017.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.02898032,-0.01457739,0.05488932,-0.00072912,0.01632666,-0.02931586,0.00362195,0.01496522,-0.03531964,-0.00225666,0.00501944,-0.10441883,0.04057295,0.01954707,0.02637058,0.00978182,-0.00331549,0.0299127,-0.08217256,0.03089866,0.08763349,-0